  "abilities": ["Stronger humanoids who encounter a manticore can cow it through intimidation and violence", " sometimes even forcing it into service as a mount. As long as the manticore is well fed with human flesh and its master leads it to victory", " a manticore mount can prove surprisingly loyal."],
