  "specials": ["Assisted Mount [one-action] Requirement The pegasus is Flying without a rider. Effect The pegasus Flies. At any point during the movement, it can allow a willing adjacent creature to Mount it. That creature must use a reaction to do so.", "Gallop [two-actions] The pegasus uses 2 move actions, each of which can be either Stride or Fly. It gains a +20-foot circumstance bonus to its Speeds during a Gallop."],
