  "size": "Medium",
  "type": "Creature",
  "specials": ["Sin Scent A sinspawn can smell creatures that reflect its sin, as the scent ability. The GM determines which creatures are appropriately sinful.", "Sinful Bite (arcane, emotion, mental) A creature hit by the jaws of a sinspawn must attempt a DC 18 Will save as it is assailed by sinful thoughts.", "Success Sickened 1.", "Critical Success Unaffected.", "Failure Sickened 2.", "Critical Failure Sickened 2 plus an additional penalty, determined by the sinspawn\u2019s sin, while it remains sickened.", "Sin A sinspawn gains an additional skill based on its sin, as well as a weapon that reflects the preferences of its kinds\u2019 ancient creators. The seven sins and the benefits they confer upon a sinspawn are noted in the Sinspawn Sins section."],
  "senses": ["Perception +10", "darkvision", "sin scent (imprecise) 30 feet"],
  "languages": ["Aklo"],
  "skills": ["Acrobatics +9", "Athletics +8", "Stealth +9", "Survival +6"],
  "abilities": ["Str +4", " Dex +3", " Con +4", " Int +0", " Wis +2", " Cha +1"],
  "items": ["one weapon determined by its sin"],
